lass=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 29, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dyv1665702621269.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dyv1665702621269.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dyv1665702621269.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dyv1665702621269\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Conditionally generate ProcScript, depending on the results of the specified\n      expressions.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__topic_d93236e1_d93237e1_d93238e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93239e1_d93240e1_d93241e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#if</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression_1</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93242e1_d93243e1_d93244e1\">... <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScript statements and precompiler directives</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93245e1_d93246e1_d93247e1\">{<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#elseif</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression_2</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93248e1_d93249e1_d93250e1\">... <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScript statements and precompiler directives</var> ...</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93251e1_d93252e1_d93253e1\">... }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93254e1_d93255e1_d93256e1\">{<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#else</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93257e1_d93258e1_d93259e1\">... <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScript statements and precompiler directives</var> ... }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93260e1_d93261e1_d93262e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#endif</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__section_x31_snc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163920e121\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93266e1_d93267e1_d93268e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>—logical expression that evaluates to true or false</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__section_szc_vnc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163920e133\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93272e1_d93273e1_d93274e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#if</span> directive conditionally\n            generates ProcScript based on the results of logical expressions. Each\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> is evaluated in sequence, beginning with the one with\n            the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#if</span> statement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93275e1_d93276e1_d93277e1\">The <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> can contain one or\n            more of the relational operators, <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> (equal to) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">!=</code>\n            (not equal to), in combination with the logical operators <code class=\"ph codeph\">&amp;</code> (and),\n            and <code class=\"ph codeph\">|</code> (or). Parenthesis can be used to create nested expressions.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__section_wqs_ync_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d163920e169\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93278e1_d93279e1_d93280e1\">The following example adds a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">debug</span>\n            statement to the ProcScript being compiled if the constant\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is defined as 1:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__pre_pxq_14c_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#ifdefined DEBUGGING\n #if (&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;=1)\n debug\n #endif\n#endif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__ul_qxq_14c_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__li_d36452e1_d36453e1_d36454e1\">If the constant\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is not defined, no further code is generated. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__li_d36455e1_d36456e1_d36457e1\">If the constant\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is defined as 0, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#if</span>\n               directive is generated as follows: <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__pre_txq_14c_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#if (1=0)\n debug\n#endif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93281e1_d93282e1_d93283e1\">In this case, no ProcScript is generated.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__li_d36458e1_d36459e1_d36460e1\">If the constant\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;DEBUGGING&gt;</code> is defined as 1, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#if</span>\n               directive is generated as follows: <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__pre_vxq_14c_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#if (1=1)\n debug\n#endif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__p_d93284e1_d93285e1_d93286e1\">In this case, the following ProcScript statement\n                  is compiled:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dyv1665702621269__pre_wxq_14c_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">debug</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612707\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612707\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "#if Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 29, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Conditionally generate ProcScript, depending on the results of the specified expressions. #if ( Expression_1 ) ... ProcScript statements and precompiler directives { #elseif ( Expression_2 ) ... ProcScript statements and precompiler directives ... ... } { #else ... ProcScript statements and precompiler directives ... } #endif Parameters Expression —logical expression that evaluates to true or false Description The #if directive conditionally generates ProcScript based on the results of logical expressions. Each Expression is evaluated in sequence, beginning with the one with the #if statement. The Expression can contain one or more of the relational operators, = (equal to) or != (not equal to), in combination with the logical operators & (and), and | (or). Parenthesis can be used to create nested expressions. Example The following example adds a debug statement to the ProcScript being compiled if the constant <DEBUGGING> is defined as 1: #ifdefined DEBUGGING #if (<DEBUGGING>=1) debug #endif #endif Copy If the constant <DEBUGGING> is not defined, no further code is generated. If the constant <DEBUGGING> is defined as 0, the #if directive is generated as follows: #if (1=0) debug #endif Copy In this case, no ProcScript is generated. If the constant <DEBUGGING> is defined as 1, the #if directive is generated as follows: #if (1=1) debug #endif Copy In this case, the following ProcScript statement is compiled: debug Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}